headline.main: FIERCER STRUGGLE IN PHILIPPINES SEEN; Resident Commissioner Here Says Loss of Manila Will Only Spur Resistance PLEDGES FIGHT TO THE END Elizalde Avers Countrymen Will Go On Beside Us Until Evil Forces Are Crushed

lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON, Jan. 2 -- Manila has fallen. This may be a disappointing development for all Americans, but it is tragic heartbreak for the people of my country.

byline.original: By JOAQUIN M. ELIZALDE Philippines Resident Commissioner in the United StatesWritten for The United Press
